<h2>About</h2>

<p>
Stating is a small weekend project that aims getting a better user interactivity with CoinShift data.
</p>

<h2>Features</h2>

After inputing your address in the "BTC Address" field Statting will automatically pool your CoinShift data, and update your charts.

<ul>
  <li>Detailed graphs</li>
  <li>CoinShift stats are updated every 1 hour</li>
  <li>Real time updates every 5 minutes (no need to refresh the browser)</li>
  <li>Background data fetch (no need to keep your browser open)</li>
</ul>

<small>
Statting keep data for a better user visualization of its history and statistics. Please note that this project is not responsible for any data loss.
</small>

<h2>Technologies</h2>

Statting is a Rails application with some background workers. In the meantime Statting is not open source, but I plan to put it on GitHub soon.

